				<h2 class="page-title entry-title">Career Opportunities</h2>
				<div class="entry-content">
										<h2>Top Reasons to Work at HAPPY Software</h2>
<h3>Corporate Culture</h3>
<p><span class="caps">HAPPY</span> offers a great work environment, challenging career opportunities and competitive compensation. Our innovative corporate culture encourages employee growth through professional training, on-the-job experience and building relationships with other company employees.</p>
<h3>Great Products</h3>
<p>We develop products and services that are innovative, easy-to-use, friendly and a great value to our clients.</p>
<h3>Excellent Benefits</h3>
<p><span class="caps">HAPPY</span> offers a benefits program that lets you choose the health, life, and disability benefits that best fits your needs and the needs of your family. <span class="caps">HAPPY</span> covers the cost to purchase some basic benefits, and you can also purchase benefits for eligible family members. Benefits include:</p>
<ul>
<li>Employer-Paid Medical Insurance for Employee</li>
<li>Dental Insurance</li>
<li>Paid Time Off</li>
<li>Profit Sharing</li>
<li>Employer-Paid Life &amp; Disability Insurance</li>
<li>401k with Strong Company-Sponsored Match</li>
<li>Tuition Reimbursement</li>
<li>Paid Holidays</li>
<li>Flextime</li>
<li>Flexible Spending Account</li>
<li>Company Sponsored Events</li>
<li>Free Onsite Parking</li>
<li>Casual Dress code</li>
</ul>
<p>We offer careers in Software Development, Technical Support, Sales, Marketing and Administration.</p>
<p><strong>Interested? <a href="mailto:resumes@happysoftware.com">Submit your resume</a></strong></p>
<h2>Open Positions</h2>
<h3>System &amp; Database Administrator</h3>
<p>As a System &amp; Database Administrator, you will administer the database and web systems for our industry-leading software for managing subsidized housing.</p>
<p>Highlights of Responsibilities:</p>
<ul>
<li>Provide oversight over HAPPY Software’s database and web systems, ensuring integrity, stability and security.</li>
<li>Monitor and benchmark database and server performance, implementing changes as needed.</li>
<li>Implement and maintain Software as a Service (SaaS) environment.</li>
<li>And more…</li>
</ul>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.happysoftware.com/downloads/pdf/JobAd_System_And_Database_Administrator.pdf" onclick="__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'download', 'https://www.happysoftware.com/downloads/pdf/JobAd_System_And_Database_Administrator.pdf');">View</a></strong> full job description. Interested?<strong> <a href="mailto:resumes@happysoftware.com">Submit your resume</a>.</strong></p>
<h3></h3>
<hr />
<h3></h3>
<h3>Web Application Developer</h3>
<p>If you are good at solving problems, attentive to details and familiar with LAMP web technologies, then you may be the perfect fit for the position of Web Application Developer at HAPPY Software.</p>
<p>Highlights of Responsibilities:</p>
<ul>
<li>Develop web applications for the subsidized housing market using proven client-side (HTML, JS, CSS, XML, jQuery, AJAX) and server-side (PHP) web technologies.</li>
<li>Ensure quality by conducting system performance tests, troubleshooting customer issues, and fixing software defects.</li>
<li>Assist with updating end user manuals and documentation.</li>
<li>Keep current with new technologies and improve your skills through ongoing training.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.happysoftware.com/downloads/pdf/JobAd_Web_Application_Developer.pdf" onclick="__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'download', 'https://www.happysoftware.com/downloads/pdf/JobAd_Web_Application_Developer.pdf');" target="_blank">View</a></strong> full job description. Interested?<strong> <a href="mailto:resumes@happysoftware.com">Submit your resume</a>.</strong></p>
<hr />
<h3>Quality Assurance Analyst</h3>
<p>As a Quality Assurance Analyst, you will design and implement test plans and quality assurance standards for our industry-leading software and services for managing subsidized housing.</p>
<p>Highlights of Responsibilities:</p>
<ul>
<li>Review, analyze and assess available documentation (user requirements, design documents, etc.) to establish<br />
product testing guidelines and use cases.</li>
<li>Test product modifications and communicate with our Development team regarding testing failures and<br />
software inconsistencies.</li>
<li>Perform beta and mission critical testing of all products and services prior to release.</li>
<li>And more…</li>
</ul>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.happysoftware.com/downloads/pdf/JobAd_QA_Analyst.pdf" onclick="__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'download', 'https://www.happysoftware.com/downloads/pdf/JobAd_QA_Analyst.pdf');" target="_blank">View</a></strong> full job description. Interested?<strong> <a href="mailto:resumes@happysoftware.com">Submit your resume</a>.</strong></p>
<h3></h3>
